WEBVTT

00:00:01.880 --> 00:00:02.606
(Previously)
Are you alright?

00:00:02.665 --> 00:00:04.350
So those guys were looking for you, Leo?

00:00:04.732 --> 00:00:05.460
I'm moving out.

00:00:05.485 --> 00:00:06.445
Where are you going to stay?

00:00:06.473 --> 00:00:06.850
That's my problem.

00:00:06.919 --> 00:00:08.169
I got his address.

00:00:08.274 --> 00:00:09.110
Do you want to go live with him?

00:00:09.137 --> 00:00:09.925
I'm sorry.

00:00:09.950 --> 00:00:11.860
Just tell me how much money you need.

00:00:11.885 --> 00:00:12.984
Keep your money.

00:00:13.956 --> 00:00:15.413
I'll take care of my brother alone.

00:00:15.783 --> 00:00:17.500
I'm sorry for the damage to the café.

00:00:17.632 --> 00:00:20.298
It's okay. What's broken, we just have to fix.

00:00:20.440 --> 00:00:21.816
Help me fix it, okay?

00:00:22.441 --> 00:00:23.908
You drank way more than you can handle.

00:00:23.933 --> 00:00:25.376
Next time, I'll just carry you home.

00:00:25.762 --> 00:00:27.442
Why go home? Sleep here.

00:00:27.518 --> 00:00:28.775
Lynx. Don't do that again.

00:00:28.814 --> 00:00:30.169
Just a goodnight kiss then.

00:00:30.541 --> 00:00:32.310
I warned you. Don't do this.

00:00:39.981 --> 00:00:42.297
Lynx, it's time to open the café.

00:00:51.374 --> 00:00:52.374
Why'd you come in?

00:00:52.399 --> 00:00:53.789
I called out for a while. No answer.

00:00:53.814 --> 00:00:54.814
I thought you were dead or something.

00:00:55.000 --> 00:00:57.598
I'm fine. Just a little hungover.

00:00:57.989 --> 00:00:59.029
Are you okay?

00:00:59.166 --> 00:01:00.186
Yeah, I'm fine.

00:01:00.841 --> 00:01:02.807
Just go set up the café. Go.

00:01:03.939 --> 00:01:05.024
Hurry and come down.

00:01:05.336 --> 00:01:06.336
Alright.

00:01:16.600 --> 00:01:17.821
Thought we were busted.

00:01:19.264 --> 00:01:21.412
Didn't I tell you to head back
before Leo woke up?

00:01:21.960 --> 00:01:23.614
How was I supposed to go back?

00:01:24.502 --> 00:01:25.815
Last night…

00:01:27.374 --> 00:01:29.028
I got pretty scratched up by this cat.

00:01:29.348 --> 00:01:31.907
Stop it. I'm going to shower now.

00:01:32.390 --> 00:01:33.926
You should hurry home.

00:01:34.036 --> 00:01:35.115
Don't let Leo see you.

00:01:36.648 --> 00:01:37.648
Wait.

00:01:39.928 --> 00:01:40.928
Why?

00:01:41.976 --> 00:01:43.255
Afraid your brother
might find out and get hurt?

00:01:43.310 --> 00:01:44.430
It's not that.

00:01:45.295 --> 00:01:48.213
I didn't mean to hide this from him.

00:01:48.950 --> 00:01:51.015
But Leo just went through
the whole thing with Dad.

00:01:51.551 --> 00:01:55.486
When the time's right,
I'll tell him myself.

00:01:55.867 --> 00:01:57.542
If you want me to keep quiet,

00:02:01.200 --> 00:02:02.406
there's got to be a price.

00:02:05.142 --> 00:02:06.314
What do you want?

00:02:07.535 --> 00:02:08.613
Drop the formalities.

00:02:09.385 --> 00:02:11.310
From now on, call me “P'.”

00:02:11.950 --> 00:02:12.950
P'Tiger.

00:02:13.331 --> 00:02:14.930
Ugh, no.

00:02:15.358 --> 00:02:16.358
Why?

00:02:17.266 --> 00:02:19.625
Just call me that.

00:02:21.048 --> 00:02:22.048
Please.

00:02:22.657 --> 00:02:23.657
Please.

00:02:24.948 --> 00:02:26.815
Fine. P'Tiger.

00:02:28.139 --> 00:02:30.817
What did you say, Nong Lynx?
I didn't hear you.

00:02:32.568 --> 00:02:33.623
P'Tiger.

00:02:33.806 --> 00:02:35.515
What did you say?
I still didn't catch it.

00:02:35.810 --> 00:02:36.743
P'TIGER.

00:02:36.777 --> 00:02:37.977
Yes, Nong Lynx?

00:02:40.528 --> 00:02:41.613
I hear you loud and clear.

00:03:43.500 --> 00:03:45.800
"Cat for Cash"
(Episode 8)

00:03:49.317 --> 00:03:50.606
Since when were you two a thing?

00:03:54.976 --> 00:03:56.028
Since the Korat trip.

00:03:56.613 --> 00:03:58.715
I made the first move.
Lynx sealed the deal.

00:04:00.693 --> 00:04:02.224
I didn't mean to keep it from you.

00:04:03.113 --> 00:04:05.713
I just wanted to find
the right time to tell you.

00:04:08.331 --> 00:04:09.868
You think that makes it hurt any less?

00:04:10.157 --> 00:04:11.986
Tiger, you have to choose.

00:04:12.099 --> 00:04:13.808
If you choose Lynx, I'll leave.

00:04:13.897 --> 00:04:16.026
But if you want me to stay,
you two have to break up.

00:04:17.784 --> 00:04:18.871
You don't need to ask.

00:04:19.800 --> 00:04:21.201
I'd choose Lynx no matter what.

00:04:21.267 --> 00:04:22.634
But you don't have to go anywhere.

00:04:25.044 --> 00:04:26.133
I'll be the one who leaves.

00:04:26.211 --> 00:04:27.211
Man!

00:04:27.763 --> 00:04:29.191
So damn handsome. So damn dangerous.

00:04:29.216 --> 00:04:30.703
Your pull is stronger than the WiFi signal.

00:04:31.084 --> 00:04:32.211
No wonder you're my brother's boyfriend.

00:04:32.267 --> 00:04:33.947
Leo! You messing with me?

00:04:34.514 --> 00:04:35.612
My room's right there.

00:04:35.712 --> 00:04:37.788
You think I didn't hear anything last night?

00:04:43.111 --> 00:04:44.212
And don't worry.

00:04:44.343 --> 00:04:46.204
Tiger's not my type.

00:04:46.421 --> 00:04:49.003
I was just flirting with him
to mess with you.

00:04:49.784 --> 00:04:52.504
My type is someone who looks smart,

00:04:53.926 --> 00:04:54.926
a little nerdy,

00:04:55.249 --> 00:04:56.818
and happens to have a medical degree.

00:04:57.742 --> 00:05:00.194
Speaking of which, I miss Dr. Pom.

00:05:00.306 --> 00:05:01.426
Go ahead and be sweet all you want.

00:05:01.543 --> 00:05:02.595
I'm taking off.

00:05:07.072 --> 00:05:08.192
You were loud.

00:05:08.799 --> 00:05:11.513
That's because
you kept scratching my back.

00:05:14.025 --> 00:05:15.602
Since Leo's giving us the green light,

00:05:16.325 --> 00:05:19.037
I can fill you up with sweetness
without worrying about anyone, right?

00:05:19.226 --> 00:05:22.092
Before that, how about filling up
the cat litter first?

00:05:23.664 --> 00:05:26.313
Work alone takes up the whole day.

00:05:26.495 --> 00:05:29.366
Who says I can't be sweet
while working?

00:05:29.422 --> 00:05:31.934
♪ Name any star you want, I'll fetch that light ♪

00:05:32.234 --> 00:05:36.013
♪ Or the sun that crowns the sky so bright ♪

00:05:37.972 --> 00:05:40.161
♪ I'll go all in, give up every chip for you ♪

00:05:40.296 --> 00:05:41.888
♪ I give it all because you're my love, one and true ♪

00:05:42.429 --> 00:05:43.895
♪ Never gonna hit the brakes ♪

00:05:43.945 --> 00:05:46.086
♪ Love you, love you, what can I do? ♪

00:05:46.621 --> 00:05:48.871
♪ Only you, just you, that's all I'm asking for ♪

00:05:48.992 --> 00:05:51.184
♪ Let me love you only, now and evermore ♪

00:05:51.214 --> 00:05:54.862
♪ You're in my heart, I'll give it all because it's you ♪

00:05:56.657 --> 00:05:58.607
♪ All in for your everything ♪

00:05:58.646 --> 00:06:00.777
♪ All in for your everything ♪

00:06:00.896 --> 00:06:03.019
♪ All in for your everything ♪

00:06:03.049 --> 00:06:05.475
♪ All in for your everything ♪

00:06:17.466 --> 00:06:19.866
"OH MEOW RICE" IS ON THE MENU TODAY!

00:06:24.840 --> 00:06:27.532
MY FAVORITE CAT

00:06:30.174 --> 00:06:31.174
What's this?

00:06:32.178 --> 00:06:34.354
I just updated our relationship status
on social media.

00:06:35.501 --> 00:06:36.501
But…

00:06:38.772 --> 00:06:39.808
can you delete it?

00:06:44.221 --> 00:06:45.221
Why?

00:06:46.506 --> 00:06:47.722
We're a couple now, aren't we?

00:06:49.412 --> 00:06:50.720
Hey!

00:06:51.046 --> 00:06:54.230
Isn't that Lynx, the café owner
who's officially off the market?

00:06:56.139 --> 00:06:57.322
First you two were fighting,

00:06:57.517 --> 00:07:00.302
and now suddenly you're in love.

00:07:01.113 --> 00:07:02.305
When did that spark happen?

00:07:02.406 --> 00:07:03.423
Can I get an interview?

00:07:07.456 --> 00:07:09.322
Hello, hello. The mic is on.

00:07:12.375 --> 00:07:13.692
My question's probably too hard.

00:07:16.280 --> 00:07:18.693
Come on, no need to be shy.

00:07:22.489 --> 00:07:24.183
He's shy. His face is turning red.

00:07:28.714 --> 00:07:29.714
Lynx.

00:07:31.162 --> 00:07:32.162
I'm sorry.

00:07:38.920 --> 00:07:40.314
I don't like being teased.

00:07:42.563 --> 00:07:44.003
I get awkward and…

00:07:45.146 --> 00:07:46.717
I don't know how to react.

00:07:47.573 --> 00:07:48.792
I'm sorry for being like this.

00:07:56.916 --> 00:07:58.607
So many friends are
texting me to tease me.

00:07:59.356 --> 00:08:01.612
That's why I don't like
sharing my personal stuff.

00:08:11.889 --> 00:08:12.929
I deleted it.

00:08:14.018 --> 00:08:17.808
I'm sorry for posting it
without asking you.

00:08:18.121 --> 00:08:21.015
Next time before I post anything,
I'll ask you first.

00:08:22.072 --> 00:08:23.072
Okay?

00:08:32.073 --> 00:08:33.396
But if anyone asks,

00:08:34.072 --> 00:08:35.458
I'll say I'm your boyfriend.

00:09:01.313 --> 00:09:03.011
Hey, have you seen this online?

00:09:04.198 --> 00:09:06.013
See what? I already deleted it.

00:09:06.121 --> 00:09:07.292
No, not that.

00:09:07.683 --> 00:09:09.698
I now know where our customers
have been going.

00:09:10.988 --> 00:09:12.814
There's a new cat café nearby.

00:09:12.931 --> 00:09:14.708
They post promo clips nonstop. Look.

00:09:18.835 --> 00:09:22.109
Whoa! They all look great.

00:09:22.382 --> 00:09:23.388
Look at that belly.

00:09:23.801 --> 00:09:25.793
You've got to be kidding.
Come on.

00:09:26.192 --> 00:09:27.604
We can't let this happen.

00:09:27.677 --> 00:09:28.684
This is our turf.

00:09:28.829 --> 00:09:31.303
We need to do promo clips to fight back.

00:09:31.603 --> 00:09:36.714
(This is Jiro, the owner of Cat-Cheer Café
and a total heartthrob.)

00:09:37.539 --> 00:09:41.400
(Gosh. When will Madame Mom
stop fixing me with some other cats.)

00:09:41.504 --> 00:09:45.188
(My name is Jenny.
Are you still hiring waitresses?)

00:09:45.270 --> 00:09:48.018
(My family's been drowning in debt.)

00:09:48.689 --> 00:09:50.307
(You don't need to work here.)

00:09:50.354 --> 00:09:54.110
(I'll hire you to be my fake wife.)

00:09:54.668 --> 00:09:56.725
(What? Me?!)

00:09:57.970 --> 00:09:58.970
What's that?

00:09:59.402 --> 00:10:03.005
Why aren't we filming the cats' daily lives
like other cafés?

00:10:03.167 --> 00:10:04.984
You don't know a thing, bro.

00:10:05.123 --> 00:10:07.123
Vertical drama is a thing now.

00:10:07.376 --> 00:10:08.786
If you don't believe me, check this out.

00:10:08.838 --> 00:10:10.684
Look. I just posted last night.

00:10:10.818 --> 00:10:12.006
The views are blowing up.

00:10:12.341 --> 00:10:13.341
Wow.

00:10:13.843 --> 00:10:17.395
I think I should go film
the Fake Date to Fool Mom episode now.

00:10:20.930 --> 00:10:22.495
I can't help but feel a little jealous.

00:10:22.634 --> 00:10:25.803
Yeah. I could never come up
with something like that either.

00:10:26.731 --> 00:10:28.411
That's not what I meant.

00:10:29.199 --> 00:10:32.222
I'm jealous of Jenny and Jiro.

00:10:33.156 --> 00:10:35.417
They get to have sweet videos
to keep as memories.

00:10:38.378 --> 00:10:39.378
Lynx.

00:10:40.369 --> 00:10:42.744
Let's film some cute clips
and post them to our Stories too.

00:10:44.247 --> 00:10:45.738
Can we?

00:10:46.200 --> 00:10:47.200
Please.

00:10:48.636 --> 00:10:49.822
It's not that you can't.

00:10:50.296 --> 00:10:53.801
How am I supposed to be sweet
when there are people all around us?

00:10:57.189 --> 00:10:59.128
Get ready to be famous.

00:11:05.150 --> 00:11:07.202
Hey, Dr. Pom's coming.

00:11:07.577 --> 00:11:08.620
What should I do?

00:11:09.826 --> 00:11:12.515
I want to film them,
but I also want to see Dr. Pom.

00:11:12.995 --> 00:11:14.195
Leave it to me.

00:11:14.573 --> 00:11:17.697
I'll make sure they look
absolutely sweet on camera.

00:11:27.710 --> 00:11:28.710
Cut!

00:11:29.129 --> 00:11:30.787
Let me send this clip to Leo to check.

00:11:37.376 --> 00:11:38.396
Are you guys tired?

00:11:39.109 --> 00:11:40.522
Your acting was impressive.

00:11:41.106 --> 00:11:42.951
I almost believed
you two were actually dating.

00:11:43.006 --> 00:11:45.704
(Oh come on. We weren't that great.)

00:11:46.282 --> 00:11:48.594
(I just followed the script.)

00:11:48.816 --> 00:11:51.991
(Love can wait. Let me focus on work first.)

00:11:53.124 --> 00:11:54.268
The footage is good to use.

00:11:54.502 --> 00:11:55.622
We can go now.

00:11:58.061 --> 00:11:59.111
Let's go, Jenny.

00:12:02.319 --> 00:12:03.381
Are you hungry, Lynx?

00:12:04.013 --> 00:12:05.106
I made you a sandwich.

00:12:15.352 --> 00:12:17.804
I'm sorry.
I didn't prepare anything for you.

00:12:18.180 --> 00:12:20.914
It's okay. There's always next time.

00:12:42.323 --> 00:12:45.243
We don't look like a couple, do we?

00:12:52.369 --> 00:12:53.369
So…

00:12:54.232 --> 00:12:55.503
what would you like me to do?

00:12:57.727 --> 00:12:58.742
I don't know.

00:12:58.942 --> 00:13:00.914
I've never been
in a serious relationship before.

00:13:01.892 --> 00:13:04.288
When we're out in public,
I honestly don't know how to act.

00:13:06.304 --> 00:13:07.304
Lynx.

00:13:10.042 --> 00:13:11.323
Can I hold your hand?

00:13:26.856 --> 00:13:28.411
Don't worry about other people.

00:13:29.760 --> 00:13:31.920
We'll take it slow and steady, our own way.

00:13:34.496 --> 00:13:35.496
Mm.

00:13:38.260 --> 00:13:40.218
I'll try to be a good boyfriend.

00:13:41.191 --> 00:13:42.510
I won't be childish with you.

00:13:44.380 --> 00:13:45.703
You don't need to try.

00:13:46.214 --> 00:13:47.267
Just be yourself.

00:13:58.734 --> 00:14:01.201
Look. Those are the cat café owners.

00:14:02.322 --> 00:14:03.322
Excuse me.

00:14:03.714 --> 00:14:06.855
Are you two the owners of
Cat-Cheer Café?

00:14:08.601 --> 00:14:09.601
Yes.

00:14:10.584 --> 00:14:13.155
Can we take a selfie with you two?

00:14:13.213 --> 00:14:15.090
We want to show this
to our friends at uni.

00:14:16.453 --> 00:14:19.297
Sorry, but how do you
know who we are?

00:14:20.089 --> 00:14:21.287
Have you been to our café before?

00:14:21.382 --> 00:14:23.649
No. We actually saw you on TikTok.

00:14:23.776 --> 00:14:25.905
Your clips are really
blowing up right now.

00:14:26.043 --> 00:14:27.843
We've been watching
your clips on loop all day.

00:14:27.910 --> 00:14:28.868
So swoon-worthy!

00:14:28.991 --> 00:14:29.996
May I ask what clips?

00:14:32.085 --> 00:14:35.457
Jiro, do it like this.
ME AND JIRO SPECIAL #TigerLynx #OurCats #Catcafe #CatCheerCafe

00:14:41.389 --> 00:14:43.352
What are you looking at?
Wanna get punched?

00:14:54.220 --> 00:14:55.220
I'm sorry.

00:14:55.768 --> 00:14:58.235
I saw Jiro and Jenny's clips blow up,

00:14:58.378 --> 00:15:00.064
so I posted some
behind-the-scenes footage.

00:15:00.288 --> 00:15:01.605
I was trying to make the cats go viral.

00:15:01.689 --> 00:15:04.036
I just didn't expect them
to make you two go viral instead.

00:15:05.696 --> 00:15:06.831
Don't worry about it, Lynx.

00:15:07.074 --> 00:15:08.085
It's only 800–900 views.

00:15:08.130 --> 00:15:09.516
No, it's not!

00:15:09.797 --> 00:15:10.917
It's 800–900K.

00:15:11.158 --> 00:15:12.763
It'll probably hit a million by tonight.

00:15:18.386 --> 00:15:19.386
I'm sorry.

00:15:19.573 --> 00:15:22.530
If I'd known you didn't like this,
I wouldn't have posted them.

00:15:23.292 --> 00:15:25.048
I'll go delete them now.

00:15:28.676 --> 00:15:29.713
Sorry, we're closed.

00:15:32.481 --> 00:15:35.608
Hey. This man is Hongtae!

00:15:36.724 --> 00:15:38.281
From the Hongtae &amp; My Master channel.

00:15:38.908 --> 00:15:40.532
He's the number one cat influencer.

00:15:41.616 --> 00:15:43.296
Number two now, actually.

00:15:43.412 --> 00:15:46.385
Everyone's talking about
the #TigerLynx hashtag now.

00:15:46.658 --> 00:15:48.354
I was hoping to ask for a collab.

00:15:48.399 --> 00:15:50.187
But if it's not a good time,
that's fine.

00:15:50.631 --> 00:15:51.711
I can come back later.

00:15:52.570 --> 00:15:53.610
Wait a minute.

00:15:53.810 --> 00:15:55.477
What kind of content
did you have in mind?

00:15:57.191 --> 00:15:59.312
Well, like other promo clips...

00:15:59.400 --> 00:16:03.008
a café review with an interview
with both owners.

00:16:03.874 --> 00:16:04.894
An interview too!

00:16:08.917 --> 00:16:09.944
I think it's a no.

00:16:10.685 --> 00:16:11.698
That's fine then.

00:16:13.569 --> 00:16:14.569
Excuse me.

00:16:17.671 --> 00:16:21.121
What's the feedback like
after each clip goes up?

00:16:22.886 --> 00:16:24.018
Most of the cafés shut down.

00:16:24.214 --> 00:16:25.214
What?

00:16:26.489 --> 00:16:29.210
They got too many customers to handle.

00:16:34.724 --> 00:16:35.890
I'm interested in the collab.

00:16:50.429 --> 00:16:51.429
Thank you.

00:16:55.982 --> 00:16:57.495
Are you sure you're okay doing this?

00:16:58.306 --> 00:16:59.927
If not, I can talk to them for you.

00:17:01.521 --> 00:17:02.521
I'm okay.

00:17:03.093 --> 00:17:04.620
I want to promote the café for Mom.

00:17:06.019 --> 00:17:07.297
If business picks up,

00:17:07.969 --> 00:17:09.239
I can pay off the debt faster.

00:17:10.967 --> 00:17:14.212
Okay. We'll do this like friends chatting.

00:17:14.524 --> 00:17:16.944
Ready? 5, 4, 3, 2…

00:17:19.380 --> 00:17:20.416
Thank you so much.

00:17:20.517 --> 00:17:22.001
Today's shoot was so much fun.

00:17:22.090 --> 00:17:23.175
The café sends up the cats.

00:17:23.344 --> 00:17:24.491
The cats send up the owners.

00:17:24.569 --> 00:17:26.142
Now the owners are sending me off.

00:17:26.849 --> 00:17:27.969
Thank you too.

00:17:28.089 --> 00:17:29.697
Today… was great.

00:17:30.865 --> 00:17:34.323
Oh, next week I'm hosting
a charity cat fashion show.

00:17:34.580 --> 00:17:37.016
I'd love to invite Jenny and Jiro
to walk in it together.

00:17:37.194 --> 00:17:38.347
Not sure if you'd be okay sending them...

00:17:38.364 --> 00:17:39.164
We are!

00:17:39.868 --> 00:17:41.901
I'm happy for the fans.

00:17:41.973 --> 00:17:44.332
They'll finally get to meet
Tiger and Lynx in person.

00:17:45.540 --> 00:17:46.540
Hold on.

00:17:47.059 --> 00:17:48.624
It's not just Jenny and Jiro?

00:17:49.025 --> 00:17:50.025
Come on.

00:17:50.212 --> 00:17:52.408
The cat owners have to be there too.

00:17:52.764 --> 00:17:54.381
And it's not just a walk.

00:17:54.733 --> 00:17:56.218
You'll need to perform something

00:17:56.330 --> 00:17:59.605
so the audience can vote
to raise money for stray cats.

00:17:59.716 --> 00:18:01.884
Sounds like fun already, doesn't it?

00:18:05.902 --> 00:18:07.791
Lynx has to look after the café.

00:18:08.386 --> 00:18:10.066
Can I go in his place?

00:18:10.198 --> 00:18:11.198
Fine by me.

00:18:11.309 --> 00:18:14.106
But I want your concept
to be about a wedding theme

00:18:14.344 --> 00:18:16.785
so it matches
Jenny and Jiro's short drama.

00:18:17.203 --> 00:18:18.373
You're okay with that, right?

00:18:22.192 --> 00:18:24.629
If the cats look this good,
imagine their owners.

00:18:24.958 --> 00:18:26.806
Okay. I think we got it.

00:18:27.345 --> 00:18:28.345
Thank you.

00:18:31.806 --> 00:18:33.705
Wow, you look great.

00:18:33.894 --> 00:18:35.900
I can't wait to see the other one.

00:18:44.106 --> 00:18:45.106
Wow.

00:18:45.234 --> 00:18:47.195
Now that you stand next to Leo,

00:18:47.354 --> 00:18:49.318
you two really look like
a couple getting married.

00:18:49.496 --> 00:18:50.944
Right, Lynx?

00:18:54.520 --> 00:18:55.520
Stop it.

00:18:55.829 --> 00:18:57.118
Let this ghost ship sink here.

00:18:58.708 --> 00:19:00.902
Tiger, go pick out the rings inside.

00:19:02.293 --> 00:19:03.106
The rings?

00:19:03.157 --> 00:19:03.965
Yeah.

00:19:04.297 --> 00:19:07.018
If there are wedding suits,
there has to be rings.

00:19:17.202 --> 00:19:18.303
This one's cute.

00:19:20.891 --> 00:19:21.891
Yes.

00:19:22.620 --> 00:19:23.645
It's kinda nice.

00:19:23.941 --> 00:19:25.108
But are you really okay

00:19:26.088 --> 00:19:27.508
with me wearing
this ring with Leo?

00:19:29.546 --> 00:19:30.546
Yes, I am.

00:19:31.403 --> 00:19:34.500
It's just a fashion show,
not a real wedding.

00:19:35.569 --> 00:19:36.930
But to me,

00:19:38.543 --> 00:19:40.036
if I have to wear this kind of suit,

00:19:41.486 --> 00:19:42.542
no matter where it is,

00:19:43.817 --> 00:19:45.460
I'd want the person
next to me to be you.

00:19:48.529 --> 00:19:50.013
We already gave him our word.

00:19:50.441 --> 00:19:51.627
We have to be professional.

00:19:52.644 --> 00:19:55.291
I don't want to act childish

00:19:55.964 --> 00:19:58.478
and make others feel uncomfortable.

00:20:00.813 --> 00:20:01.853
I don't know.

00:20:02.284 --> 00:20:06.385
Sometimes I want you
to be a little childish with me too.

00:20:08.973 --> 00:20:10.013
How's it going?

00:20:10.175 --> 00:20:11.398
Have you picked the rings yet?

00:20:11.766 --> 00:20:14.516
I will let the professional decide then.
This is not my thing.

00:20:22.530 --> 00:20:23.635
Have you gone to sleep yet?

00:20:25.032 --> 00:20:26.032
Not yet.

00:20:26.176 --> 00:20:27.194
What's up? Come in.

00:20:37.249 --> 00:20:38.312
What's wrong with you?

00:20:38.973 --> 00:20:41.406
Aren't you usually asleep by now?

00:20:43.136 --> 00:20:46.702
I just wanted to ask about the show.

00:20:49.320 --> 00:20:52.630
So what are you two going to perform?

00:20:54.468 --> 00:20:56.012
Tiger can play piano,

00:20:56.989 --> 00:20:58.315
so we're going to sing together.

00:20:58.471 --> 00:21:02.777
Ah. Sounds nice.

00:21:07.831 --> 00:21:08.831
So…

00:21:15.041 --> 00:21:16.223
is the bed comfortable?

00:21:17.173 --> 00:21:19.686
I've been sleeping on it for a week
and you're only asking now?

00:21:20.864 --> 00:21:23.412
If you've got something to say,
just cut to the chase.

00:21:26.973 --> 00:21:28.065
It's about Tiger, right?

00:21:30.229 --> 00:21:32.746
Mm… here's the thing.

00:21:35.333 --> 00:21:36.915
I don't want to be childish,

00:21:37.143 --> 00:21:38.818
but my boyfriend wants me to be.

00:21:38.958 --> 00:21:40.908
And you know what
the most childish thing is?

00:21:41.009 --> 00:21:42.693
Right now I feel like I'm being childish.

00:21:44.188 --> 00:21:45.283
You really don't need to worry about that.

00:21:45.513 --> 00:21:47.231
No matter how hard
you try to keep it cool,

00:21:47.587 --> 00:21:48.788
you're still childish.

00:21:48.971 --> 00:21:49.971
Hey.

00:21:51.032 --> 00:21:52.390
That didn't come from me, though.

00:21:53.509 --> 00:21:54.932
Do you want to know who said that?

00:21:57.793 --> 00:21:58.891
Lynx.

00:21:59.360 --> 00:22:01.370
Lynx, get up and eat this congee first.

00:22:01.395 --> 00:22:02.703
Then you can take your medicine.

00:22:02.814 --> 00:22:03.760
Leave it there, Mom.

00:22:03.785 --> 00:22:04.504
Let me sleep.

00:22:04.529 --> 00:22:06.088
Come on. Get up.

00:22:06.126 --> 00:22:07.433
You need to take your medicine.

00:22:07.472 --> 00:22:09.306
You're sick.
You need to take medicine.

00:22:09.412 --> 00:22:11.063
Come on, Mom.

00:22:11.977 --> 00:22:14.007
This is congee from a famous shop.

00:22:14.570 --> 00:22:15.700
This much ginger!

00:22:16.102 --> 00:22:18.251
You know I don't like ginger.

00:22:20.619 --> 00:22:23.995
It helps chase the sickness away.

00:22:24.040 --> 00:22:25.385
Fine, I'll pick it out for you.

00:22:25.490 --> 00:22:28.155
You know you get sick easily,

00:22:28.200 --> 00:22:29.625
yet you still went out in the rain.

00:22:29.876 --> 00:22:33.101
But the seniors asked me
to help with the cutouts.

00:22:33.247 --> 00:22:35.324
You can't say no to them,
but keep saying no to me?

00:22:35.606 --> 00:22:38.597
When you're sick, do those guys
pick the ginger out for you?

00:22:40.564 --> 00:22:43.405
I'll do it for you.
I'll feed you too.

00:22:44.465 --> 00:22:45.771
I'll feed you.

00:22:45.840 --> 00:22:46.722
I can eat it on my own.

00:22:46.747 --> 00:22:48.834
Come on. Let me do it.

00:22:50.717 --> 00:22:52.125
That was a long time ago.

00:22:52.459 --> 00:22:54.621
Why didn't she tell you
any of my other good stories?

00:22:55.027 --> 00:22:56.105
But Mom also said

00:22:57.177 --> 00:22:59.228
she liked it when you
acted childish with her.

00:23:02.205 --> 00:23:04.018
It made her feel like a mother.

00:23:05.669 --> 00:23:07.272
There aren't many people on this planet

00:23:08.240 --> 00:23:09.888
you could act that way with.

00:23:11.361 --> 00:23:13.821
Tiger wants you to be childish with him too.

00:23:17.759 --> 00:23:19.208
It probably makes him feel

00:23:20.982 --> 00:23:22.004
that you love him.

00:23:32.577 --> 00:23:33.577
Pa,

00:23:35.085 --> 00:23:36.085
can I join you?

00:23:36.110 --> 00:23:37.110
Go ahead.

00:23:37.991 --> 00:23:41.607
Hey, I heard
you and Lynx are official now.

00:23:42.937 --> 00:23:46.501
When are you going to
introduce him to your mom?

00:23:46.864 --> 00:23:50.832
If you wait any longer,
she might set you up with someone else.

00:23:54.104 --> 00:23:56.091
Hey, easy.

00:23:56.420 --> 00:23:57.494
Hey! That's expensive.

00:23:59.827 --> 00:24:01.507
What's wrong with you?

00:24:02.082 --> 00:24:03.082
Pa.

00:24:05.348 --> 00:24:07.348
I friggin' hated myself today.

00:24:14.780 --> 00:24:17.100
Today I unintentionally said
something hurtful to him.

00:24:21.668 --> 00:24:22.668
I know…

00:24:24.050 --> 00:24:25.212
he loves me.

00:24:27.044 --> 00:24:28.724
But I'm just not sure

00:24:31.379 --> 00:24:32.422
if our love is equal.

00:24:33.167 --> 00:24:35.223
How long have you two been together?

00:24:37.029 --> 00:24:38.046
Almost a month.

00:24:40.328 --> 00:24:41.501
This morning…

00:24:42.625 --> 00:24:44.626
your mom and I
were still sulking at each other.

00:24:46.395 --> 00:24:48.002
Two people raised differently,

00:24:48.647 --> 00:24:53.206
when they live together,
it takes time to adjust.

00:24:58.369 --> 00:25:00.049
I want to make him happy.

00:25:03.932 --> 00:25:05.747
But I ended up starting
an argument with him.

00:25:07.374 --> 00:25:08.892
Don't be afraid of arguments.

00:25:09.220 --> 00:25:12.412
As long as you still love each other
and never let go of each other's hands,

00:25:14.477 --> 00:25:20.001
you'll always come to a better
understanding of each other in the end.

00:25:48.409 --> 00:25:50.698
Oh, you're here, Tiger?

00:25:51.021 --> 00:25:52.310
I'll go get the cats ready.

00:25:55.596 --> 00:25:56.596
Today…

00:25:58.091 --> 00:26:00.221
you have a check-up appointment
for Granny Juu, right?

00:26:03.222 --> 00:26:04.262
Do your best.

00:26:07.092 --> 00:26:08.092
Mm.

00:26:10.352 --> 00:26:13.107
Sorry that I can't be there
to cheer you on today.

00:26:14.751 --> 00:26:15.751
Well…

00:26:22.391 --> 00:26:23.831
take this instead.

00:26:38.162 --> 00:26:39.911
So the song Leo and I have to sing…

00:26:42.623 --> 00:26:43.721
is a love song.

00:26:44.453 --> 00:26:45.817
I asked to change it.

00:26:47.889 --> 00:26:49.704
But they wanted it
to match the outfit theme.

00:26:51.216 --> 00:26:52.050
Mm.

00:26:52.294 --> 00:26:53.294
We're ready.

00:26:53.339 --> 00:26:55.120
Let's get going
or we'll miss registration.

00:27:00.780 --> 00:27:02.981
I'm heading out then.

00:27:37.114 --> 00:27:38.411
Hey, I forgot the ring.

00:27:38.573 --> 00:27:40.306
I told Tiger to go register first.

00:27:42.803 --> 00:27:43.803
Leo.

00:27:46.790 --> 00:27:48.532
Can I be childish just for a day?

00:28:08.120 --> 00:28:09.594
CONTESTANT WAITING AREA

00:28:14.579 --> 00:28:17.212
Hey, where's Leo?

00:28:17.584 --> 00:28:18.624
The show's about to start.

00:28:21.348 --> 00:28:22.713
I still can't get a hold of him.

00:28:23.609 --> 00:28:24.684
I'll keep trying.

00:28:25.032 --> 00:28:26.102
Alright. Hurry up.

00:28:28.861 --> 00:28:31.293
Speaking of the groom, there he is.

00:28:31.343 --> 00:28:32.350
What a relief.

00:28:32.439 --> 00:28:34.036
I'm sorry. Traffic was bad.

00:28:34.093 --> 00:28:35.175
We've got everyone, right?

00:28:35.377 --> 00:28:36.628
I'll go check on the stage.

00:28:36.653 --> 00:28:37.756
See you up there.

00:28:38.126 --> 00:28:39.126
Okay.

00:28:41.470 --> 00:28:43.116
How'd it go?
Did you find the ring?

00:28:45.916 --> 00:28:46.956
No, I didn't.

00:28:47.950 --> 00:28:49.723
I'll go rent one nearby.

00:28:50.208 --> 00:28:52.263
If they come looking for us,
you go get ready first.

00:28:53.078 --> 00:28:54.078
Okay.

00:29:18.133 --> 00:29:20.016
(We really don't look like a couple, do we?)

00:29:20.396 --> 00:29:22.615
(I've never been in
a serious relationship before.)

00:29:22.995 --> 00:29:25.727
(I honestly don't know how to act
when we're out in public.)

00:29:26.504 --> 00:29:28.221
(Don't worry about other people.)

00:29:28.684 --> 00:29:31.226
(We'll take it slow and steady, our own way.)

00:29:31.446 --> 00:29:33.305
(I'll try to be a good girlfriend.)

00:29:33.417 --> 00:29:34.823
(I won't be childish with you.)

00:29:34.848 --> 00:29:36.501
Jiro, Jenny.

00:29:37.168 --> 00:29:38.514
Are you two secretly dating?

00:29:38.629 --> 00:29:39.629
(Uh oh!)

00:29:43.180 --> 00:29:45.677
Where, when, how?

00:29:45.963 --> 00:29:49.931
(Well, almost a month now,
since the day the café got wrecked.)

00:29:50.140 --> 00:29:53.352
(At the time, I was shaken.
I cried and didn't know what to do.)

00:29:53.431 --> 00:29:55.801
(Jiro lent me his back to wipe my tears.)

00:29:55.990 --> 00:29:58.797
(So I… caught feelings for him.)

00:30:00.886 --> 00:30:02.507
Why does the plot sound familiar?

00:30:04.183 --> 00:30:05.235
Why didn't you tell me?

00:30:05.288 --> 00:30:07.414
(Jenny was afraid of getting teased.)

00:30:08.189 --> 00:30:10.693
(You also didn't tell us
about you dating Lynx either.)

00:30:10.958 --> 00:30:11.961
So you all knew?

00:30:11.994 --> 00:30:13.312
(I'm not stupid. Come on.)

00:30:13.407 --> 00:30:15.087
(What Lynx does for you…)

00:30:15.250 --> 00:30:17.705
(isn't any different from what
Jenny does for me.)

00:30:25.857 --> 00:30:26.920
Are you ready, Tiger?

00:30:27.087 --> 00:30:28.811
The cats are already waiting on stage.

00:30:29.438 --> 00:30:30.482
Leo's not here yet.

00:30:30.574 --> 00:30:33.921
Oh, he's getting ready
by the side of the stage.

00:30:34.484 --> 00:30:35.512
You'll see him up there.

00:30:36.553 --> 00:30:37.553
Okay then.

00:30:54.068 --> 00:30:57.733
Next up is the show from the cat café
that's trending right now.

00:30:57.990 --> 00:31:01.630
Please give it up for Cat-Cheer Café!

